message.body: Hey, you going to the US Open or what?
No can do
You?
I'm streaking the course!
Nah, just kidding.
But I am renting out my, and my neighbors driveway for parking.
Made $80 today. Hopefully more on Saturday.
I saw that on FB
What's keeping you away?
Better coverage on TV and Traffic
Also trying to keep up with you MapMyrun
Yeah, it's kind of cool watching it on TV. Every time they say "the sun just came out again" I feel like they're reporting on my life!
You should sign up for Everymove.org (or .com), I've been earning $5 Amazon Gift cards just for exercising. It syncs with MapMyRun.
Are you running ever day yet? Today will be 256 of the streak.
If you feel like coming by Saturday or Sunday, we've got some street parking passes (selling driveway space)
Is your tree still looking for a home?
I mix up the runs with Muay Thai and gym. I try to get in a good 8-10 mile run once a week too. Also tried paddle boarding the other weekend. I forget to log stuff or don't take my phone.
Gift cards sound good
Yeah, I saw you're getting dangerous!
Quit smoking couple months back and now all I wanna do is work out
Good move!
Goal is to get into a triathlon or two by end of summer
That's a good goal.
Is that tree of yours still looking for a home?
Yep he's struggling
I think we have a good spot for him if the offer still stands!
